 <h1>
   <a href="/search?q=X-Men%3A+Days+of+Future+Past"><strong class="highlight">X-Men:</strong> Days of Future Past</a>
   (PG-13)
 </h1>

 <p class="section">
	<strong class="fr" style="margin-left:10px">131 minutes</strong>

	
    
    	 
   	
    	 
   	
    	 
   	
    	 
   	
	<a href="/statistics/movies/by_genre/action-adventure">Action/Adventure</a> | <a href="/statistics/movies/by_genre/comic-book-adaptation">Adapted (Comic Book)</a> | <a href="/statistics/movies/by_genre/superhero">Superhero</a> | <a href="/statistics/movies/by_genre/sequel">Sequel</a>
	 | <a href="/statistics/3d-release-calendar">3D Movie</a>
	
   		&nbsp; - &nbsp; <span class="published">May 23, 2014</span>
	
 </p><!-- .section -->


 
 
	
	
 
	
	
 
	
	
 
	
	
 
 
 	<p class="section">
		<span style='white-space:nowrap'><strong>Opening Weekend:</strong> $90,823,660 </span> | <span style='white-space:nowrap'><strong>Total Domestic Gross:</strong> $233,921,534</span> | <span style='white-space:nowrap'><strong>Worldwide Gross:</strong> $748,348,506</span> | <span style='white-space:nowrap'><strong> Total Budget*:</strong> $275,000,000</span>
 	</p>
 
