  <div class="views-field views-field-field-header">        <div class="field-content">Field Experiences</div>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Faculty reported on whether the classes they taught had field experiences and, if not, whether the classes would benefit from the addition of this feature.</p>
</div>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-field-bubble-image">        <div class="field-content"></div>  </div>  
